# Example values for REQUIRED, NON-secret variables (no default in variables.tf).
# Copy to terraform.auto.tfvars and fill in real values -- do NOT commit that file.
#
# Sensitive variables are deliberately NOT listed here. Supply them via:
#   - TF_VAR_<name> environment variables, or
#   - a gitignored *.auto.tfvars file, or
#   - your CI/CD pipeline's secret store (GitHub Actions secrets, Vault, etc.)
#
# Sensitive variables used by this project:
#   sql1_administrator_password  (export TF_VAR_sql1_administrator_password=... )
#   sql2_administrator_password  (export TF_VAR_sql2_administrator_password=... )

